Enter the Pokémon Stadium—Ready for Battle!
Build two decks from a powerful set of components—and then play right away, with this two-player Build & Battle Stadium set! Get ready to face your opponents with the Pokémon TCG: Sword & Shield—Fusion Strike Build & Battle Stadium!

• 2 individual Build & Battle Boxes, each containing a 23-card Evolution pack to build your decks
